### 1. Tạo danh mục Ăn uống (Expense)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nấu ăn",
  "type": "EXPENSE",
  "icon": "food",
  "color": "#FF0000"
}

### 2. Tạo danh mục Lương (Income)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lương tháng",
  "type": "INCOME",
  "icon": "money",
  "color": "#00FF00"
}

### 3. Lấy danh sách danh mục
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 4. Xóa danh mục (Thay ID vào)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/categories/276d9134-9bc3-49ab-963e-17adc5d925c5
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}